sg":"放心 呢個情況只會更差<br />\n我係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時酗酒到唔返工唔想見人<br />\n脾氣仲差 連你都打埋"},{"pid":"8d72e893f90cf98b21ee059b3d851d1279bb7465","tid":739281,"uid":79865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"一啲自制能力都冇既人唔值得結婚<br />\n而家鍾意你就對你好姐，對耐左感情淡左應該會表露本性"},{"pid":"ae4244f934046e63ac6704c32abf8cfe4192f7ce","tid":739281,"uid":5309,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cfbc723f95dac2856d9759e1649ef96dc030bb17","tid":739281,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"今日戒唔到<br />\n或者已經有咁既問題 <br />\n<br />\n仲諗結婚<br />\n將來結左婚 一有工作唔如意就郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比多次機會 靜心同佢傾下 <br />\n睇你咁講佢都係初初開始 未算酗酒 只係發酒癲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"咁應該係發酒癲 <br />\n佢又無話唔飲唔得 但有酒都多數會嗌<br />\n我好心軟 因為好愛佢 <br />\n希望真係會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b92576a59704e67098307953f3a299451d24d85","tid":739281,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f43d383f1ebd1ee23c03c99806fc520d38b99b","tid":739281,"uid":129506,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"依家都咁，遲啲生埋小朋友飲醉酒打尻個仔就係哩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得世界仲有咁多家暴，根本一個願打一個願捱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"我老豆就係咁 雖然無出手打<br />\n但發酒瘟都好撚煩<br />\n根本呢種人自制力好差"},{"pid":"50f90fe3b48c53f9e514d0484c7bdb420362405c","tid":739281,"uid":1993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"你心中根本就已經有答案<br />\n但你就次次事後都心軟<br />\n你一世做捱打嗰方吧"},{"pid":"7c4f8a3a50628a91516e4da9881013028d7146d1","tid":739281,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"好彩我渣到連飲一技細啤都頭暈姐<img src=\"/assets/faces